  "story": "Every Saturday, four friends run neighbouring stalls at the riverside craft market, watched over by old Tomas, who has kept the market ledger for forty years and still records every sale in green ink. This week each friend brought a different handmade craft and settled on a different price. Tomas has misplaced the ledger page - match every friend to the craft they made and the price they charged.",
